  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::QuestionData
  question: 'BigTech deployed a new mobile app to its customers and as a result has
    generated much more data about customers than before.

    What characteristic
    of big data does this scenario describe?'
  questionId: 7
  answers:
  - Veracity
  - Velocity
  - Volume
  - Variety
  - Value
  maxSelections: 1
  correctAnswerIndices: 02000000
  correctMessage: In this scenario, the amount of data has grown in quantity after
    deploying the new mobile app.
  incorrectMessage: Not quite. In this scenario, consider how adding another source
    of data affects the quantity of data.
